課程概述 Course Description
       教授運輸系統基本組成單元與互動關係，同時以宏觀的角度探討運輸系統與經濟活動及都市發展之關係，使學生具備分析運輸問題與研擬改善方案的能力，同時培養學生獨立思考與運輸專業技能。For the students to understand the dynamic fields of transportation by providing them with a solid background and history of transportation that emphasizes the fundamental role and importance the industry plays in our society.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    Graduates should solve strategic problems with a creative and innovative approach.
Graduates should possess a global economic and management perspective.
Graduates should possess the necessary skills and values demanded of a true professional.    

