課程概述 Course Description
       本課程旨在深入探討智慧型運輸系統與車輛資通訊系統(Telematics), 將會對個別系統的設計概念、發想、考量與細節做深入探討，並以實際ITS系統設計當做教材與上課同學探討。
This course aims to introduce special topics in Intelligent Transportation Systems and telemaics systems. We will discuss the special issues of the sub-systems in ITS with emphasis on design concepts, ideas, consideration, implementation details, and system workflows. Several real ITS system or trial projects on each sub-system in ITS will be introduced in detail. Technical and institutional issues associated with implementation of ITS or telematics applications will be discussed.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
gain in-depth knowledge on ITS, including ATMS, ATIS, ETC, CVO, Telematicsknow that how does a ITS application be designed and implementedrealize the design consideration in each ITS sub-systemsgain the trend and knowledge on VANET, and discuss the VANET applications 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Syllabus, Introduction to ITS2ITS overview , Current development of ITS in worldwide and in Taiwan3ITS overview, Telematics overview4Technologies in ITS (including communication, positioning, etc.)5Traffic Information：VD / GVP / EVP / CVP6Traffic Information：VICS, IVP7National Holiday8Special topic on Advanced Vehicle Control and Safety Service9Special topic on Advanced Public Transportation System10Midterm Exam (or Speech)11Special topic on Advanced Traveler Information System 12Special topic on Advanced Traffic Management System13Discussions on other ITS sub-systems (EMS, EPS, CVO, IMS, AHS)14Discussions on other ITS sub-systems (EMS, EPS, CVO, IMS, AHS)15Special issues on Vehicle Ad-Hoc Network16Special issues on Vehicle Ad-Hoc Network17Term Project Report18Final Exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


